modName: Naomi Wood Elf Racemenu face preset
summary: A pretty Wood Elf Preset, hope you like her!
descriptionHtml:
[center][/center][center]﻿[font=Georgia][size=5][b]Naomi

[/b][/size][/font][font=Times New Roman][size=3]MY SCREENIES ARE NOT GREAT BUT THATS BECAUSE I DO NOT HAVE THE BEST COMPUTER.
Please share your Screenshots! I'd love to see!

Since i have a guilty pleasure of  humanish elves with visible big pointy ears, i decided i wanted to share my favorite girl with you guys.
[/size][/font][font=Times New Roman][size=3]Now this is a WOOD ELF preset but i saw she is just as nice looking if you load her preset as a Nord.


HOW TO INSTALL PRESETS:

I HIGHLY ADVICE YOU TO MANUALLY INSTALL
Where does the JSLOT file go?:
Go to where you installed your skyrim/Data/SKSE/Plugins/CharGen/Presets <-- Drop it there

Where does the .NIF and .DDS File go?:
Go to where you installed your skyrim/Data/SKSE/Plugins/CharGen <--- Drop it there
